  "text": "Appropriate mesh size is crucial for model simulation. When the grid size is halved, the discretization error may fall to a quarter, while the calculation time will increase by nearly 16 times and the storage requirement will increase by eight times [CITATION_1] . In order to determine the appropriate mesh size in this model, the normalized power absorption (NPA) of the treated material has been used to complete mesh independent studies [CITATION_2] .",
